title: Symphony Communication Signs Deal With Dow Jones
text:
Symphony Communication Services LLC, the instant-messaging software company backed by several of Wall Streetâ€™s biggest firms, has signed a deal with Dow Jones & Co. to provide news content on its service, people familiar with the matter said.
